N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 19 ยง 177.11 - Auditing

State Regulations
A duly authorized designee of the department may audit any
course offered and may verify attendance and inspect the records of attendance
of the course at any time during its presentation or
thereafter. Notes
